==English==
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
#One who attempts to use false or exaggerated pretenses to get their way, particularly in [[politics]], by instilling in the [[population]] an unnecessarily high level of [[fear]].
#:''George Bush is commonly perceived among the international community to be a prime example of a '''fear monger'''.''

===Verb===
#To engage in such acts.
#:''Did you see the latest ad by [[w:Tom Tancredo|Tom Tancredo]] tying Mexican immigrants to al Qaeda? What a load of '''fear mongering'''!''